Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女性絕跡於Altair 原本只能坐以待斃的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了抓住一線生機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了對Vega的調查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始計劃捕獲能夠承受Altair生物環境的女性--Rare Iger
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並使其成為孕育我們星球的未來的夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此被選出來的其中一名候選者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便是貪睡的夏娃 艾麗西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她由於時空轉移的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直處於假死狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無蘇醒的跡像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而如今她已經是二手貨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們暫時返回Altair的期間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她竟然生下了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並將其留在了Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這些都是瑣碎之事罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她算不上是真正的夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能像這樣持續地沉眠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.76,0:04:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淪為只為安撫你的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無翅的蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安撫我?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多可悲啊 出雲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無翅蝴蝶的鱗粉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只是如夢似幻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 不如干脆…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.55,0:04:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給漫長的夢境畫上句號
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:04:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許你對艾麗西亞動手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼出雲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼了結這場夢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓Jin潛入機械天使的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能確定出操縱那機體的Rare Iger
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎 出雲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Vega 蝴蝶有著復活的含義
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連那不被允許的愛也將再度復活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不·羈·野·獸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就是這樣 神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釋放更多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釋放出你心中那瘋狂而又不容抗拒的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹底地 毫無保留地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快喚醒沉睡於你體內的有關阿波羅和希爾菲的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲就在你心中那觸手可及之處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那芬芳的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那甜美的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會為你帶來非凡的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她那溫熱的指引下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛將屢獲新生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 你在渴求愛的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想完成禁斷的合體對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更多地…更多地渴求吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更多地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為愛咆哮的飢渴野獸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 愛的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了平息你心中的飢渴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著只屬於你的愛展開旅途吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野獸?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出雲 我想復活的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是什麼能編織Altair未來的Rare Iger
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是沉睡在Vega的創聖的機械天使
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 就給我記住一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不打算相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再發生什麼事 到時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我一定會把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那力量到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿克巴爾金·巴德巴艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 不許再企圖潛入女生宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪炎 對同學以槍相向的你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在裡面多反省一段時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.90,0:10:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…聽說你好像喜歡艾莉西亞 所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是艾莉西亞?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點差異…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你看看側臉...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷漠的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿克巴爾金·巴德巴艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.41,0:10:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是假冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼問題也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過Neo DEAVA的最終入學考試的是他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我校需要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷絕的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚葉說過她能理解Jin的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 他身上雖然有很多謎團
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不像是壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.65,0:11:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能跟他相處得更融洽一點 交談更多一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相理解更多一點就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 能互相理解多一點就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃 我對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有想知道的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有想詢問的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關那個人的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關那個男人的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人的眼神有點寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要說原諒那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來就像棄犬一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 隊伍真長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 兩個人都一副悶悶不樂的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好 忘了買果汁…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 能讓我喝一口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公…公然猥褻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 這不是間接接吻麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,間接接吻?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 也讓我喝一口你那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑西卡 你真的很渴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼在機庫裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把門關上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓神樂前往Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:13:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我為你的啟程飾以鮮花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後只要你希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妨以你那忽明忽滅的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去照耀創聖的機械天使
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你 不管再怎麼口渴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能在眾目睽睽之下做出那種不知羞恥的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往水壺裡倒些大麥茶吧 大麥茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡大麥茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就紅茶 烏龍茶 總之什麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 那種行為...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回宿舍去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 你下午的課怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 傑西卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我給裙子的下擺鎖縫了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}才初學不久 做得還不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 真夠青澀的啊 受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.79,0:14:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jin要是能就此融入集體的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別裝得事不關己似的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人都如饑似渴地想得到愛情的滋潤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看傑西卡不就如饑似渴了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…你突然說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把御子乃心靈的地下水脈挖出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是被禁止戀愛的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.95,0:14:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與Abductor的戰鬥一結束不就毫無問題了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前必須先做好預約
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說預約?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃多可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再這樣慢條斯理的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.09,0:14:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒準她會被其他人搶走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃 能耽誤你一點時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就行動起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是挖洞三兄弟的老二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.96,0:15:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是自立心旺盛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓失去理性的你前往Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈有此理!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上從Mithra上下來 回到出雲大人身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:15:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別妨礙我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出雲大叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我把Iron Sea夷為平地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是死了條心 乖乖地把門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要選哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}第四區Iron Sea受損 周邊居民 請立即到指定避難避難
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 神樂的戰鬥能力會在急劇上漲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逆季綻放 瞬時凋零
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其花之名為神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.05,0:16:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出雲 你明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是站在愛的那一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方機體已退離射線攻擊範圍 隨時可開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮擊開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把臭女人交給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 神樂 奉上你的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.11,0:18:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和御子乃到底有什麼不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿波羅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個 你找我有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.93,0:18:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的…那個傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被搶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.54,0:18:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是那樣 就是…有點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 能請你看著那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…不是現在馬上開始也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到與Abductor的戰鬥結束之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妨試吼一聲吧 神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使愛如今不在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要高聲呼喚 就能改變一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就能夠扭轉乾坤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被揍的感覺 好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准動 神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭 好想殺死那個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死她…將她擁入懷裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.24,0:21:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.79,0:21:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.37,0:21:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那力量究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.46,0:22:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未影 是你這傢伙幹的好事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說得這麼難聽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.48,0:22:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是 神樂的野性的蒙召
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.54,0:22:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 出發吧 神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著愛的新天地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------ED part1----------
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.96,0:24:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天看過的電影 那就是我們的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.90,0:24:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起來 從那以後我總是飄起來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.61,0:24:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.39,0:24:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 Aquaria舞動於空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------------------------------------
